By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 7
  Paragraph: 13
Title: Fit For Emperors And Kings
---
The next day Lieh Tzu brought the shaman to see Hu Tzu. When they had
left the room, the shaman said, "I'm so sorry - your master is dying!
There's no life left in him - he won't last the week. I saw something
very strange-something like wet ashes!"
